{"books":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"type":"pdf","official":false,"author":"张迪杰","files":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/maoquanji28.pdf"],"article":{"title":"给邹普勋的信","alias":"","parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"给邹普勋的信"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"（1950年5月15日）普勋兄："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五月七日来信收到，感谢你的好意。贵体渐愈，甚慰。尚望好生保养。你家里人口多少，生活困难至何种程度，你自己还能劳动否，便时尚望告我。此祝健康"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九五○年五月十五日[1]邹普勋，毛泽东少年时的私同学和邻居。"}],"authors":["毛泽东"],"dates":[{"year":1950,"month":5,"day":15}],"is_range_date":false,"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":395,"page_end":395},"tags":[{"name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"},{"type":"文稿类型","name":"书信"}]}]}